<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r,1" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><gap extent="13" reason="illegible" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="??"/>αἱρέσι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="??"/><choice><corr>φορέτρο</corr><sic><expan>φολετρο<ex cert="high">υ</ex></expan></sic></choice> <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="??"/><expan>διανο<ex cert="high">μῆς</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">ἀρουρῶν</ex></expan> <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 
</ab></div><div n="r,2" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><gap extent="14" reason="illegible" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἡρακλε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ίδης Σαρ</supplied>απίωνι τῶι ἀξιολογωτάτῳ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>Δημήτριος ὁ γνωστὴρ ἠξίωσέν με <choice><corr>λέγειν</corr><sic>λ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εγ</unclear>ιν</sic></choice> σοι 

    <lb n="3"/>ὥστε αὐτὸν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἄ</unclear>λυπον γενέσθαι <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>πὲρ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τῶν</unclear> π<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ροτέρ</unclear>ων 

    <lb n="4"/>ἐτῶν. λέγει γὰρ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὅτι</unclear> ὠφέλησα αὐτὸν μεγάλως καὶ 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐν τῇ ἀννώνῃ. λέγει δὲ ὅτι ἀνν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ώ</unclear>ν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νῦ</unclear>ν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ζητεῖτ</unclear>αι. 

    <lb n="6"/>εἰ οὖν πάλιν δύνῃ ἐκπλέξαι παρὰ σεαυ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τῷ</unclear>, τύχῃ 

    <lb n="7"/>τῇ ἀγαθῇ. εἰ δὲ μή γε, ἐπίστειλον τί θέλεις ἑτοι-

    <lb n="8"/>μασθῆναι. ἀλλὰ μὴ ἀμελήσῃς, οὔπω γὰρ <choice><corr>ἐξῆλθον</corr><sic>εξηλθαν</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐὰν <hi rend="diaeresis">ἰ</hi>σχύσῃς <del rend="erasure">ἄ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λλῳ</unclear></del> ἐκπλέξαι, μέγα ἔργον ποιεῖς, 

    <lb n="10"/>διότι κτήνη οὐκ ἔχομεν οὐδὲ χοίρους. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε ὁλοκλη<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied>οῦντα 

    <lb n="12"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>ὔχομαι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notBefore="0320" precision="low" type="textDate">nach ca. 320</date></p></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL X, S. 142. Rückseite: spätes III.</p></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1490</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">31747</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1490</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;12;1490" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">142</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" type="nome">Oxyrhynchites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.31747" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://www.igl.ku.dk/~bulow/Oxy1490.jpg"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>